void TcpTestSocket::OnAsyncEvent (  Event  event  )  [protected, virtual]
 

Triggered by one of following events on TCP socket:

c_event_data_received - when data is received in TCP protocol, read this data and if this is test packet mark it as received and continue with receiving other packets. If this was last packet that should be received in this test, send a message to application.

c_event_data_sent - when packet was sent, send a message to application

Reimplemented from InetSocket.
